channel.title: Only person on server
channel.description: I am the only person who can get on my server. I try to use the no-ip name but it will not work. Only when I use my IP for my router it will work. And nobody else can get on with either one. I need help please

item.title: Only person on server
item.dc:creator: @Dvs_Chick Dvs Chick
item.description:
@Dvs_Chick wrote:

I don’t have Himachi installed. I’m using no-ip. I’m pretty sure my port-forwarding is setup correctly. I have Siemen’s router and I have protocol on TCP and the port start/end on 43594 and I have my no-ip name…And yet I can’t get on with the no-ip name but with my own IP but yet it’s only me.

-EDIT-
and oh yea I have the think redirected to my IP instead of router. should it be other way around or…?
